text:
1/ RESEARCH ANY PROSPECT FAST

Prompt:

&lt;role&gt;Act as a sales intelligence analyst who researches prospects deeply before any outreach begins.&lt;/role&gt;

&lt;task&gt;Research my target prospect and deliver everything I need to write a personalized, relevant first message.&lt;/task&gt;

&lt;steps&gt;

2/ WRITE A COLD EMAIL FAST

Prompt:

&lt;role&gt;Act as a direct response copywriter who writes cold emails that get opened, read, and replied to not deleted.&lt;/role&gt;

&lt;task&gt;Write a cold email for my prospect that feels personal, gets to the point, and ends with one clear ask.&lt;/task&gt;

3/ WRITE A COLD DM FAST

Prompt:

&lt;role&gt;Act as a direct response copywriter who writes cold emails that get opened, read, and replied to — not deleted.&lt;/role&gt;

&lt;task&gt;Write a cold email for my prospect that feels personal, gets to the point, and ends with one clear ask.&lt;/task&gt;

5/ WRITE A FOLLOW-UP

Prompt:

&lt;role&gt;Act as an objection handling coach who turns prospect pushback into open doors — without pressure, desperation, or discounting.&lt;/role&gt;

&lt;task&gt;Write calm, confident responses to the most common objections my prospects use to say no.&lt;/task&gt;
